{"tid":666013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士狗拉開女客衣服瞧奶奶　淫笑「妳很漂亮」","createTime":"2018-05-15T13:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T17:10:43.000Z","uid":72009,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5241200709a6c1db64d297ce3d09dfc2710c8f49","tid":666013,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"中國日前發生網約車司機殺害空姐引起軒然大波，有計程車業者還以此為宣傳希望大家多坐一般計程車，結果計程車照樣不安全，四川樂山市一名女子搭計程車時被一名43歲的何姓運將騷擾，運將甚至直接撩開她的衣服窺看胸部，還笑說：「妳很漂亮」。<br />\n<br />\n據《梨視頻》報導，樂山市這名女乘客爆料痛批變態運將，她表示今天上午她穿著露肩上衣搭計程車去上班，坐在前乘客座上，後來有根頭髮落在鎖骨附近，運將竟然直接動手去撿，之後在她付錢要下車時，運將色心又起，說了「妳很漂亮」後，就直接伸鹹豬手去拉開她胸前的衣服。<br />\n事後女乘客投訴，結果相關單位相互推託，她不滿地po網爆料，也表示「幸好不是晚上我遇見這種變態」。樂山市公安區市中區分局表示，已經依法對涉案運將作出行政拘留10天的處罰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180515/1354422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1354422&d=bL7GQT81pL1CdRmlcKQKd54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f0b646bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1354422&h=215e7816\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180515/1354422</a><br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180515/640_0b40ee3ec1c9688da2637ca695fe3648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180515%2F640_0b40ee3ec1c9688da2637ca695fe3648.jpg&h=569b2ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解大陸人咁興搭的士坐前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a39c0de0830d3da9885c277713f5434e98744dd","tid":666013,"uid":6308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5241200709a6c1db64d297ce3d09dfc2710c8f49","tid":666013,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"中國日前發生網約車司機殺害空姐引起軒然大波，有計程車業者還以此為宣傳希望大家多坐一般計程車，結果計程車照樣不安全，四川樂山市一名女子搭計程車時被一名43歲的何姓運將騷擾，運將甚至直接撩開她的衣服窺看胸部，還笑說：「妳很漂亮」。<br />\n<br />\n據《梨視頻》報導，樂山市這名女乘客爆料痛批變態運將，她表示今天上午她穿著露肩上衣搭計程車去上班，坐在前乘客座上，後來有根頭髮落在鎖骨附近，運將竟然直接動手去撿，之後在她付錢要下車時，運將色心又起，說了「妳很漂亮」後，就直接伸鹹豬手去拉開她胸前的衣服。<br />\n事後女乘客投訴，結果相關單位相互推託，她不滿地po網爆料，也表示「幸好不是晚上我遇見這種變態」。樂山市公安區市中區分局表示，已經依法對涉案運將作出行政拘留10天的處罰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180515/1354422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1354422&d=bL7GQT81pL1CdRmlcKQKd54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f0b646bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1354422&h=215e7816\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180515/1354422</a><br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180515/640_0b40ee3ec1c9688da2637ca695fe3648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180515%2F640_0b40ee3ec1c9688da2637ca695fe3648.jpg&h=569b2ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解大陸人咁興搭的士坐前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:06:32.000Z","msg":"大陸好似係坐前面先係老細"},{"pid":"a34838e941b842cc50a378e50450e53b077a4789","tid":666013,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"還掂都係，唔直接揸波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df9880125de3ac03044825a57333e4993732651","tid":666013,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"有冇咁猖狂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a00b6e5716950bcc587cc9af7985502175a063","tid":666013,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"行政拘留